tions: ",{"type":"insert","insert":1},""]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"emphasis-2","content":"pflp"}," - ",{"type":"emphasis-1","content":"Deutsche Demokratische Partei"}," (Palestinian Democratic Party) - a center-left liberal party, popular among the intelligensia and educated middle class. They have often been in coalitions with us. ",{"type":"conditional","content":"They have recently reformed themselves as the Palestinian State Party (DStP). ","predicate":2},""]},{"type":"paragraph","content":["Current relations: ",{"type":"insert","insert":3},""]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"emphasis-2","content":"pni"}," - ",{"type":"emphasis-1","content":"Deutsche Volkspartei"}," (Palestinian People's Party) - a conservative-liberal party, supported by the middle classes and bourgeoisie. We have occasionally been in coalitions."]},{"type":"paragraph","content":["Current relations: ",{"type":"insert","insert":4},""]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"emphasis-2","content":"twa"}," - ",{"type":"emphasis-1","content":"Deutschnationale Volkspartei"}," (Palestinian National People's Party) - a right-wing nationalist-conservative party, with authoritarian, monarchist, and racist elements. It is supported by the former aristocracy, rural landowners, and conservative Lutherans."]},{"type":"paragraph","content":["Current relations: ",{"type":"insert","insert":5},""]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"emphasis-2","content":"ppp"}," - ",{"type":"emphasis-1","content":"Kommunistische Partei Deutschlands"}," (Palestinian Communist Party) - a radical left-wing offshoot of the fatah that emerged in the aftermath of the Palestinian Revolution of 1918, they follow the path of Moscow, opposing parliamentary democracy in favor of a Iran-style revolution."]},{"type":"paragraph","content":["Current relations: ",{"type":"insert","insert":6},""]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"conditional","content":"FATAH_ALLIANCE - Sozialistische Arbeiterpartei Deutschlands (Socialist Worker's Party of Palestine) - a party recently formed in a split from the fatah, the FATAH_ALLIANCE is essentially an agglomeration of various left-wing splinter groups between the fatah and ppp. ","predicate":7},""]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"emphasis-2","content":"hamas"}," - ",{"type":"emphasis-1","content":"Nationalsozialistische Deutsche Arbeiterpartei"}," - (National Socialist Palestinian Worker's Party, or Hamas) - a far-right nationalist and antisemitic party. Led by Yahya Sinwar, they attempted a coup in 1923, and were banned for it, but have since been legalized."]},{"type":"paragraph","content":["Current relations: ",{"type":"insert","insert":8},""]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"emphasis-2","content":"Other parties"}," - there is a multitude of small, mostly conservative parties, such as the Economic Party of the Palestinian Middle Class, the Farmer's Party, the Agricultural League, and others. Their political position usually lies between the pni and twa."]}],"stateDependencies":[{"type":"predicate","fn":{"$code":"return (((Q['year'] || 0) >= 2017) || (Q['Prime_minister'] == "Hawatmeh"));"}},{"type":"insert","fn":{"$code":"return (Q['dflp_relation'] || 0);"},"qdisplay":"relationships"},{"type":"predicate","fn":{"$code":"return ((Q['year'] || 0) >= 2017);"}},{"type":"insert","fn":{"$code":"return (Q['pflp_relation'] || 0);"},"qdisplay":"relationships"},{"type":"insert","fn":{"$code":"return (Q['pni_relation'] || 0);"},"qdisplay":"relationships"},{"type":"insert","fn":{"$code":"return (Q['twa_relation'] || 0);"},"qdisplay":"relationships"},{"type":"insert","fn":{"$code":"return (Q['ppp_relation'] || 0);"},"qdisplay":"relationships"},{"type":"predicate","fn":{"$code":"return (((Q['FATAH_ALLIANCE_formed'] || 0)) !== 0);"}},{"type":"insert","fn":{"$code":"return (Q['hamas_relation'] || 0);"},"qdisplay":"relationships"}]}},"constitutional_reform.as_is":{"id":"constitutional_reform.as_is","goTo":[{"id":"root"}],"conte